  "title": "ARCHITECTURAL DRAFTER",
  "description": "<ul><li>Liaise with and assist customer /engineers / supervisors / coordinators to develop conceptual design to 2D or 3D drawing.</li><li>Responsible for updating working drawing as issued by project/ sales department.</li><li>Able to read and interpret engineering drawings.</li><li>Responsible to prepare shop drawings, as-built drawing, cut size drawing for submission and approval.</li><li>model for site preparation works and construction works.</li><li>Able to multi-task drafting works with reasonable time and ad hoc duties as assigned.</li><li>Ensure design / drawings meet relevant code compliance requirements and good engineering practices.</li></ul><p>For interested applicants, please apply online or send your resume in WORD format to <strong>davidnhbsg@gmail.com; ram@deshingroup.com; wayne@deshingroup.com; shawn@deshingroup.com</strong></p><p>Thank you for your application but we regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified</p>",
